image is a critical componet to run the container. this image is read only template it has necessary application binary and dependencies.
this images ever run to make it run we have to create a container. once you inside the container there will be writeable layer where you write your extra code
writeable layer only work during the container active if you restart the container data will be lost to you avioud this data lose we use docker volume
temparary data will be stored in writeable layer 
